short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple utility to automatically change the Stop Loss and Take Profit of your PrimeXBT positions for you.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: When using it, you'll obtain Trailing Stop Loss and Trailing Take Profit functionality. This extension is only valid and useful until PrimeXBT decides to implement it themselves.
